### 发送短信验证码
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/send-sms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138000"
}

###

### 短信验证码登录（首次登录-自动注册）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login/sms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "code": "123456"
}

###

### 密码登录（需要先设置密码）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### 登出
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 测试受保护的接口（需要 Token）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/agent/simple/chat?message=你好
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
